{
  "texts": [
    "Additionally, cybersecurity threats must be considered, as hackers targeting AVs could gain control over operations and endanger passengers and other road users.",
    "Robust cybersecurity measures should be implemented to prevent such risks.",
    "Furthermore, privacy concerns of AV drivers require attention, with clear guidelines and safeguards to protect personal information collected by autonomous vehicles.",
    "Moreover, the reliance on infrastructure and connectivity challenges widespread adoption and effectiveness.",
    "Consistent and reliable support, including road markings, traffic signals, and communication networks, is vital for successfully integrating autonomous technologies on a large scale."
  ]
}